    .terms_content
      %p
        This following document sets forth the Privacy Policy for GradReady Pty. Ltd. ("GradReady"),
        %a{:href => "/"} gradready.com.au
      %p GradReady is committed to providing you with the best possible customer service experience. GradReady is bound by the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth), which sets out a number of principles concerning the privacy of individuals.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Security
      %p This website supports Secure Socket Layers of 128bit and greater.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Collection of your personal information
      %p There are many aspects of the site which can be viewed without providing personal information, however, for access to future GradReady customer support features you are required to submit personally identifiable information. This may include but not limited to a unique username and password, or provide sensitive information in the recovery of your lost password.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Sharing of your personal information
      %p The information is used to enhance the vistor's experience when using the website to display personalised content. E-mail addresses and login details will not be sold, rented or leased to 3rd parties.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Use of your personal information
      %p For each visitor to reach the site, we expressively collect the following non-personally identifiable information, including but not limited to browser type, version and language, operating system, pages viewed while browsing GradReady website, page access times and referring website address. This collected information is used solely internally for the purpose of gauging visitor traffic, trends and delivering personalized content to you while you are at this site.
      %p From time to time, we may use customer information for new, unanticipated uses not previously disclosed in our privacy notice. If our information practices change at some time in the future we will use for these new purposes only, data collected from the time of the policy change forward will adhere to our updated practices.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Changes to this Privacy Policy
      %p GradReady reserves the right to make amendments to this Privacy Policy at any time. If you have objections to the Privacy Policy, you should not access or use the Site.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Accessing Your Personal Information
      %p You have a right to access your personal information, subject to exceptions allowed by law. If you would like to do so, please let us know. You may be required to put your request in writing for security reasons. GradReady reserves the right to charge a fee for searching for, and providing access to, your information on a per request basis.
    .terms_content
      %h3 Contacting Us
      %p
        GradReady welcomes your comments regarding this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy and would like further information, please raise a query via
        %a.ask_ques_sec{href: "javascript:void(0)"} support.

